@model RealEstateWebUI.Areas.admin.Models.Customer
@using (Html.BeginForm(null, null, FormMethod.Post, new { id = "formEditOverview", novalidate = "novalidate", autocomplete = "off" }))
{
<div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">X</button>
            <h4 class="modal-title">Sửa thông tin về khách hàng</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">                    
                    @Html.ValidationSummary(true)
                    @Html.HiddenFor(x => Model.CustomerID)
                    <div>
                        @Html.LabelFor(model => model.CustomerFirstName, new { @class = "control-label strong" })
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.CustomerFirstName, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Nhập họ" })
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div>
                        @Html.LabelFor(model => model.CustomerLastName, new { @class = "control-label strong" })
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.CustomerLastName, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Nhập tên" })
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
                    <div class="" style="margin-top: 10px">
                        @Html.LabelFor(model => model.CustomerEmail, new { @class = "control-label strong" })
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.CustomerEmail, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Nhập email" })
                        @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.CustomerEmail)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12" style="margin-top: 10px">
                    <div class="">
                        @Html.CheckBoxFor(model => model.AcceptsMarketing)
                        @Html.LabelFor(model => model.AcceptsMarketing, new { @class = "control-label" })
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Đóng</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="submitEdit(@Model.CustomerID)"> Xác nhận</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="~/Scripts/jquery.validate.js"></script>
<script src="~/Scripts/jquery.validate.unobtrusive.js"></script>
<script src="~/assets/js/admin/customer.js"></script>
}